Leaflet code

The World map from the tmap library is drawn using Leaflet. After merging the World data with df with the COVID-info, we can draw a map with markers and the travel restrictions in the pop-ups.

World %>% 
    leaflet(width="100%") %>% 
    addTiles() %>% 
    addMarkers(data = World, lng = ~X, lat = ~Y,
               popup = ~paste0("<h4>", name, "</h4>",
                    "International restrictions: ", optional2, "<br>",
                    "<small>Published: ", ymd(optional1), "</small>"
                               ),
               group = "Travel restrictions")
